      "step": 1,
      "title": "输出文字",
      "description": "cout << \"Hello\"; 把字符串 \"Hello\" 输出到屏幕。<< 是插入运算符，方向指向 cout，表示数据流向屏幕。",
      "codeLine": "cout << \"Hello\";",
      "highlights": ["cout", "<<", "Hello"],
      "state": {
        "variables": [],
        "containers": [],
        "output": "Hello"
      }
    },
    {
      "step": 2,
      "title": "输出变量的值",
      "description": "声明变量 score = 95，然后用 cout << score; 输出变量的值。注意变量名不加引号，输出的是变量的值而不是字母。",
      "codeLine": "int score = 95;\ncout << score;",
      "highlights": ["score", "cout"],
      "state": {
        "variables": [
          {"name": "score", "value": "95", "note": ""}
        ],
        "containers": [],
        "output": "Hello\n95"
      }
    },
    {
      "step": 3,
      "title": "用 << 连续输出",
      "description": "cout 可以用多个 << 拼接输出内容。这里把文字和变量拼在一起输出，让结果更易读。",
      "codeLine": "cout << \"分数是\" << score << \"分\" << endl;",
      "highlights": ["<<", "score", "endl"],
      "state": {
        "variables": [
          {"name": "score", "value": "95", "note": ""}
        ],
        "containers": [],
        "output": "Hello\n95\n分数是95分"
      }
    },
    {
      "step": 4,
      "title": "输出表达式结果",
      "description": "cout 也可以直接输出表达式的计算结果，不需要先存到变量里。这里输出 score + 5 的值。",
      "codeLine": "cout << \"加 5 分后：\" << score + 5 << endl;",
      "highlights": ["score + 5"],
      "state": {
        "variables": [
          {"name": "score", "value": "95", "note": "score 不变"}
        ],
        "containers": [],
        "output": "Hello\n95\n分数是95分\n加 5 分后：100"
      }
    }
